/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />經過上次既教訓 ,今次開post唔只有我個價,仲會加上其他商戶既價錢作比較(例如:<span style=\"color: teal;\">香港終端</span>,<span style=\"color: orange;\">Price</span>,<span style=\"color: brown;\">Amazon</span>),方便大家格價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果巴打有更多的報價來源歡迎留言提供,希望入黎既巴打都以最抵價買到最想要既產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我提供既報價主要係顯示咭,不時會有notebook,monitor甚至Keyboard,Mouse等周邊,總之有平就會PO。<br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"cea1587ee92b0d883974794549dff31d4bdc64a6","tid":611240,"uid":68805,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">節日限定</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>即日至4月1日愚人節<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">MSI</span></span> Gaming Notebook[/red] 來貨價賣機!</ins></em></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">重要! ! !<br />\n<ins>買家須知</ins>:</span></span></em> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">於2018年度,Intel 處理器已經進入第八世代。<br />\n雖然現時市面上仍未有第八代遊戲處理器,但綜合網上消息可推斷,比起第七代(4核),第八代處理器(6核)的表現比第七代強30%左右。所以,現時不適合追求極限性能的玩家入手。<br />\n<br />\n不過,聽聞今次換代主要係處理器的提升,而顯示卡則繼續沿用GEFORCE&reg; GTX 10 系列。假如你願意接受七代四核心處理器,以換取一個較優惠的價錢,咁今次會係你入手的好時機。</span><br />\n</strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(I7-7700HQ vs I7-8750H )</span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">非官方數據</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://cpu.userbenchmark.com/Compare/Intel-Core-i7-8750H-vs-Intel-Core-i7-7700HQ/m470418vsm211019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcpu.userbenchmark.com%